description:
This match was shot before a live audience and was streamed live to members on February 27th.
If you were a member at the time, you had the opportunity to watch this live from home. Today we present you the edited, downloadable version for those who missed it or did not watch the streaming live feed.
Congratulations to Team Black, the 2008 Tag Team Champions. This was an amazing match: hard fought, and incredibly brutal. 36 minutes of tough wrestling, followed by the defeated team getting fucked in front of a live audience.
